Package: usb-imagewriter-ng
Version: 0.4
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Discreete Linux Team <info@discreete-linux.org>
Installed-Size: 366
Depends: coreutils (>= 6.10-3), procps, gksu, python, pv, python-parted, python-pyudev
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: Improved USB Image Writer, tool to write .img files to USB Keys
 A GUI to write .img files like the ones created by the
 ubuntu-mobile team for UME to a USB Key for installing
 the image to mobile devices and netbooks.
 Improved version of the original USB Image Writer.
 Comes with the following advantages:
 * Check image size vs. media size before writing
 * Optional verification pass
 * Improved error control
 * Can be used from the command line (for scripting)
